PiPo SDK release v0.1

   3 Jul , 2015

   Update: the PiPo SDK v0.2 is now available on Ircam R&D‘s GitHub!

   The PiPo module API for writing your own processing and analysis
   objects is now available and documented here:
   http://recherche.ircam.fr/equipes/temps-reel/mubu/pipo
   It includes an example xcode project to build a simple pipo mxo for Max
   that also works within MuBu.

   api, mubu, pipo, sdk

