First Prize of the Margaret Guthman Musical Instrument Competition

   22 Mar , 2011

   The MO from the Interlude project won the First Prize of the Margaret
   Guthman Musical Instrument Competition at Georgia Tech’s Center for
   Music Technology.

   Read the review on CreateDigitalMusic: “Human Gestures Power Winners of
   Guthman Competition“
